      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Streaking Shadow",
        "Client": "Fledgling Investigator",
        "Description": "I was out exploring in the Flooded\r\nForest, when suddenly, lightning\r\nstruck. I looked to the sky and saw\r\nsomething zipping and zapping\r\nfrom tree to tree! I got away some-\r\nhow, but others might not be so\r\nlucky. Please, do something!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Ombre foudroyante",
        "Client": "Enqu\u00EAteur en herbe",
        "Description": "J\u0027explorais la For\u00EAt inond\u00E9e,\r\nquand la foudre a frapp\u00E9. J\u0027ai\r\nlev\u00E9 la t\u00EAte et j\u0027ai vu un\r\ntruc sauter d\u0027arbre en arbre !\r\nJ\u0027ai r\u00E9ussi \u00E0 m\u0027enfuir, mais\r\ntout le monde n\u0027aura pas cette\r\nchance. Fais quelque chose !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ombre striscianti",
        "Client": "Investigatore in erba",
        "Description": "Stavo esplorando la Foresta\r\ninondata, quando ho visto un\r\nlampo. Ho guardato il cielo e\r\nho notato qualcosa che\r\nzigzagava tra gli alberi! Sono\r\nfuggito, ma altri potrebbero\r\nnon riuscirci. Fa\u0027 qualcosa.",
        "Target": "Caccia un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Streichender Schatten",
        "Client": "Nachwuchsermittler",
        "Description": "Als ich im Flutwald unterwegs\r\nwar, schlug ein Blitz ein. Ich\r\nsah auf und da war eine Krea-\r\ntur, die von Baum zu Baum\r\nh\u00FCpfte! Ich bin ihr entkommen,\r\naber andere haben vielleicht\r\nkein Gl\u00FCck. Bitte tu etwas!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Tobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Sombra voladora",
        "Client": "Investigador principiante",
        "Description": "Exploraba el Bosque inundado\r\ncuando cay\u00F3 un rayo. Luego...\r\n\u00A1vi algo saltando de \u00E1rbol en\r\n\u00E1rbol! Logr\u00E9 huir, pero otros\r\npodr\u00EDan correr peor suerte.\r\nPor favor, \u00A1haz algo!",
        "Target": "Caza un Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
